{"type": "article", "id": 13934, "title": "手工木刻蓝牙音箱", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-25T07:33:30Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 32, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000254PWStNxoq07MZwjIr.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一系列来自夏威夷的蓝牙音箱，每一只按照不同的主题，由艺术家专门打造。音箱取材自夏威夷的桃木，在北卡设计和手工制作完成，每一只都是独一无二的。音箱可以蓝牙与其他设备连接，一块 12V，2200 mAh 的可充电电池供电，看上去时尚但又充满复古气息。这是<a href=\"http://www.thewoodenboombox.com/collections/boomboxes\" target=\"_blank\">购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261416069a5qKsZkVfBEoGrL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.54400978\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141607Z7T3Vs14nE9OJMxW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.700489\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141607GNcPM0SaoY8CmKWv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.700489\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141608HtV6Z4usdhoQ3bkM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.700489\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141608gs5WV1IHFfKR4aOu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.700489\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141609iqIEd73s8zoVb9l6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.700489\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141609Aut0SiNUoBkJjwF8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.700489\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141610DZytFsQTcOo4Sd8x.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.700489\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141611BwGRS3NftKUj2E89.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.700489\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141612FCcBYtpONmXRgUWQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.700489\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141613lzJ8UOibm4VtqsQx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.700489\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}